&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This is a senior individual contributor opportunity for someone who enjoys hands-on engineering, automation, cloud-native technologies, and solving complex platform challenges while working alongside multidisciplinary teams delivering innovative solutions for leading financial institutions.&lt;/p&gt;
